@startuml
!include <C4/C4_Context>
' !include C4-PlantUML/C4_Context.puml
!theme cloudscape-design
skinparam backgroundColor #black
skinparam defaultFontColor #white
/'
C1 – System Context Diagram

Purpose:
Shows the Software System under consideration as a black box, and how it
interacts with human users (*People) and other software systems (*Software Systems).

*People:
- Authenticated User: views sensor data and manages account via browser
- Administrator: manages the system and users via browser

*Software Systems:
- System: IoT Sensor Network API (includes API and Database containers)
- External System: Browser (used by people to interact with the API)
- External System: IoT Gateway (aggregates and forwards sensor data)
- External System: IoT Sensors (send data to the gateway)

*Relationships:
- People -> Browser: Use to interact with the system
- Browser -> System: Sends requests and receives data
- IoT Sensors -> IoT Gateway: Send telemetry data via local protocol
- IoT Gateway -> System: Forwards aggregated data

'/

Person(user, "Authenticated User", "Views sensor data and manages account via browser")
Person(admin, "Administrator", "Manages the system and users via browser")

System(iot_system, "IoT Sensor Network API", "Provides API endpoints for sensor data collection and management. Includes API and Database.")

System_Ext(browser, "Browser", "Web interface used by people to interact with the API")
System_Ext(gateway, "IoT Gateway", "Aggregates and translates sensor data for the API")
System_Ext(sensors, "IoT Sensors", "Hardware devices that collect telemetry data")

Rel(user, browser, "Uses")
Rel(admin, browser, "Uses")
Rel(browser, iot_system, "Sends requests and receives data", "HTTPS/JSON")
Rel(sensors, gateway, "Send telemetry data", "Zigbee/BLE/LoRa")
Rel(gateway, iot_system, "Forwards data", "MQTT/HTTPS")

@enduml
